  "description": {
    "en": {
      "provenance": "imported",
      "value": "The project will be implemented in 2 districts, 2 municipalities by 2 national NGOs implementing partners. The project will engage 10 staff from the implementing partners and  3 INCLUDED Nepal staff. \r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\r\n\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\tThe total cost of the project for 3 years (2014-2016) will be USD 532,885.\r\n\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\tAll components of the project will be run through the platform of a Community Center in or near migrant settlements in the identified areas. The components of the project are:\r\n\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t1. Early childhood development\r\n\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t2. After School Program\r\n\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t3. Family Education\r\n\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t5. Vocation and Life skills\r\n\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t6. Research and Advocacy"
    },
    "ne": null
  },
